8
00:01:51,879 --> 00:01:53,200
I didn't come here looking for

9
00:01:53,200 --> 00:01:54,019
any favors.

10
00:01:54,819 --> 00:01:55,799
I just realized I might

11
00:01:56,060 --> 00:01:57,019
have feelings for you.

12
00:02:02,079 --> 00:02:02,780
It's no big deal.

13
00:02:03,260 --> 00:02:04,400
Honestly, I can't even tell

14
00:02:04,400 --> 00:02:05,019
if this is

15
00:02:05,019 --> 00:02:06,420
admiration or dependency,

16
