but to me,

17
00:02:07,620 --> 00:02:08,379
it is what it is.

18
00:02:08,659 --> 00:02:10,099
Even if Miao Jing were here,

19
00:02:10,379 --> 00:02:10,819
I still

20
00:02:10,819 --> 00:02:11,879
needed to say it out loud.

21
00:02:16,340 --> 00:02:16,800
I'm sorry,

22
00:02:18,500 --> 00:02:19,259
but I don't

23
00:02:20,139 --> 00:02:20,900
see you that way.

24
00:02:25,460 --> 00:02:27,311
I saw this coming before I even walked in,

25
00:02:28,400 --> 00:02:29,300
but I just felt like

26
00:02:29,300 --> 00:02:30,680
I had to get it off my chest.

27
00:02:30,960 --> 00:02:32,340
Feels better now that it's out.

28
00:02:39,740 --> 00:02:41,099
I'll put these in the fridge, yeah?

29
00:02:42,280 --> 00:02:43,300
Make sure you

30
00:02:43,300 --> 00:02:44,319
deal with them,

31
00:02:44,419 --> 00:02:46,060
before they go bad again.

32
00:02:58,099 --> 00:02:59,319
You're taken good care of.

33
00:02:59,979 --> 00:03:00,939
Anyway, I gotta go.

34
00:03:04,120 --> 00:03:04,479
Tu Li.

35
00:03:08,939 --> 00:03:09,919
If you ever need a hand,

36
00:03:11,580 --> 00:03:12,219
let me know.

37
00:04:10,030 --> 00:04:10,977
Aren't Xiao Yu and Ma Yang

38
00:04:11,240 --> 00:04:12,155
supposed to be with you?

39
00:04:12,220 --> 00:04:13,355
Still packing up.

40
00:04:13,560 --> 00:04:14,340
They'll be here in a minute.

41
00:04:15,620 --> 00:04:16,480
Got a memo today.

42
00:04:16,480 --> 00:04:18,200
Hongshen's breathing down our necks

43
00:04:18,390 --> 00:04:19,200
