44
00:04:19,939 --> 00:04:20,740
What's the rush?

45
00:04:23,500 --> 00:04:25,180
The foreign trade landscape is shifting.

46
00:04:25,699 --> 00:04:26,740
They probably want to strike

47
00:04:26,740 --> 00:04:28,040
while the iron's hot in Gangcheng

48
00:04:28,560 --> 00:04:29,622
and get this locked down ASAP.

49
00:04:31,100 --> 00:04:32,259
Once the papers go out,

50
00:04:32,500 --> 00:04:33,844
