Mr. Cen?

588
00:34:00,200 --> 00:34:00,779
You got married?

589
00:34:01,559 --> 00:34:03,079
Since when is marriage the only thing

590
00:34:03,079 --> 00:34:04,259
worth celebrating to a woman?

591
00:34:04,500 --> 00:34:05,400
I bought a house, okay?

592
00:34:06,319 --> 00:34:06,960
Congrats!

593
00:34:07,380 --> 00:34:08,420
Right back to you.

594
00:34:09,500 --> 00:34:10,739
Once we're back in Haicheng,

595
00:34:10,739 --> 00:34:11,300
come over

596
00:34:11,300 --> 00:34:12,179
to enjoy hot pot

597
00:34:12,460 --> 00:34:13,579
at my place.

598
00:34:13,739 --> 00:34:14,099
Sure.

599
00:34:14,099 --> 00:34:15,340
It's a deal.

600
00:34:15,440 --> 00:34:17,300
Girl, you ate.

601
00:34:17,300 --> 00:34:19,519
When will I ever buy a house?

602
00:34:20,360 --> 00:34:21,679
Aren't you a local?

603
00:34:22,519 --> 00:34:23,059
I am.

604
00:34:23,619 --> 00:34:24,699
My parents wanted

605
00:34:24,699 --> 00:34:25,679
to give me

606
00:34:25,679 --> 00:34:26,300
one of theirs.

607
00:34:26,380 --> 00:34:28,019
But Mr. Cen, you know,

608
00:34:28,179 --> 00:34:29,260
I don't want it.

609
00:34:29,679 --> 00:34:30,420
Otherwise,

610
00:34:30,480 --> 00:34:31,900
I'd be under their thumb on

611
00:34:32,099 --> 00:34:32,940
everything from job

612
00:34:32,940 --> 00:34:33,699
to marriage.

613
00:34:34,059 --> 00:34:35,320
Once I triggered them, well,

614
00:34:35,500 --> 00:34:36,199
they'd be like

615
00:34:36,840 --> 00:34:38,059
"We gave you the house,

616
00:34:38,300 --> 00:34:39,239
don't you be ungrateful."

617
00:34:50,860 --> 00:34:52,099
These styles

618
00:34:52,099 --> 00:34:53,619
are pretty trendy.

619
00:34:54,420 --> 00:34:55,559
Girls love them.

620
00:34:56,880 --> 00:34:58,159
Could you try it on for me?

621
00:34:58,320 --> 00:34:58,760
Sure.

622
00:35:00,340 --> 00:35:01,820
It is trendy,

623
00:35:02,880 --> 00:35:04,179
but I feel like this

624
00:35:04,179 --> 00:35:05,460
would be uncomfortable.

625
00:35:05,619 --> 00:35:06,239
Sweetie,

626
00:35:06,480 --> 00:35:07,059
really,

627
00:35:07,119 --> 00:35:08,699
you don't have to ask me.

628
00:35:08,860 --> 00:35:10,320
You know best

629
00:35:10,320 --> 00:35:11,340
what your daughter likes.

630
00:35:13,079 --> 00:35:14,699
Hi, I want to see this one.

631
00:35:15,920 --> 00:35:16,780
Take your time.

632
00:35:16,840 --> 00:35:17,699
I'll be right back.

633
00:35:17,699 --> 00:35:18,300
Sure.

634
00:35:19,420 --> 00:35:20,119
This one?

635
00:35:20,119 --> 00:35:21,539
Mom, I want the bunny one.

636
00:35:22,820 --> 00:35:24,159
Aiming high, huh?

637
00:35:24,579 --> 00:35:26,059
Did you see the price?

638
00:35:26,679 --> 00:35:28,059
You can't back out now.

639
00:35:28,539 --> 00:35:29,380
We agreed

640
00:35:29,380 --> 00:35:30,780
it was my heirloom gold piece.

641
00:35:31,179 --> 00:35:31,820
I'm picking

642
00:35:31,820 --> 00:35:32,920
what I want.

643
00:35:33,739 --> 00:35:34,579
Fine, fine.

644
00:35:35,199 --> 00:35:36,019
Guess I was

645
00:35:36,070 --> 00:35:37,222
born to pay for your debts.

646
00:35:38,079 --> 00:35:39,039
As a mother,

647
00:35:39,079 --> 00:35:40,780
you'll do anything for your daughter.

648
00:35:41,179 --> 00:35:41,900
I'll take it.

649
00:35:42,159 --> 00:35:43,039
Thanks, Mom.

650
00:35:52,739 --> 00:35:53,340
Young lady,

651
00:35:53,340 --> 00:35:54,333
you have really slim wrists.

652
00:35:54,440 --> 00:35:55,511
Perfect for bracelets.

653
00:36:01,539 --> 00:36:02,380
How about this one?

654
00:36:05,300 --> 00:36:06,360
Oh, stop it.

655
00:36:07,760 --> 00:36:08,380
Honey...

656
00:36:08,380 --> 00:36:08,860
Young lady,

657
00:36:08,860 --> 00:36:09,619
would you like to

658
00:36:09,619 --> 00:36:10,539
look at anything else?

659
00:36:11,199 --> 00:36:12,820
I'll wait at the crossing.

660
00:36:12,820 --> 00:36:13,340
How about this one?

661
00:36:13,440 --> 00:36:14,719
No, thanks.

662
00:36:18,119 --> 00:36:18,579
Of course.

663
00:36:18,579 --> 00:36:19,300
Try it on.

664
00:36:21,880 --> 00:36:22,579
Jing,

665
00:36:23,159 --> 00:36:23,900
I've got something

666
00:36:23,900 --> 00:36:24,699
to take care of.

667
00:36:25,260 --> 00:36:25,780
I need you

668
00:36:25,780 --> 00:36:27,159
to take the bus home.

669
00:36:27,840 --> 00:36:28,380
And...

670
00:36:28,380 --> 00:36:29,079
Sorry,

671
00:36:29,079 --> 00:36:30,019
we'll be back in a few days.

672
00:36:30,019 --> 00:36:30,360
Okay.

673
00:36:30,900 --> 00:36:31,619
Take care.

674
00:36:33,380 --> 00:36:34,579
Anything you like?

675
00:36:50,300 --> 00:36:52,260
If the budget is tight,

676
00:36:52,260 --> 00:36:53,420
we have some pendants.

677
00:36:53,579 --> 00:36:54,900
We can string them up,

678
00:36:54,900 --> 00:36:55,820
it'll look just as good.

679
00:36:55,980 --> 00:36:56,400
No.

680
00:36:57,139 --> 00:36:57,940
It has to be gold.

681
00:36:58,119 --> 00:36:59,440
And it can't be light.

682
00:36:59,760 --> 00:37:01,199
I haven't seen my girl in ages.

683
00:37:01,900 --> 00:37:02,380
Okay.

684
00:37:31,539 --> 00:37:32,019
Hello.

685
00:37:32,519 --> 00:37:34,460
The number is switched off.

686
00:37:34,780 --> 00:37:36,059
Please try later.

687
00:38:37,659 --> 00:38:38,679
Jing, why are you still here?

688
00:38:39,860 --> 00:38:41,059
Teacher, I

689
00:38:41,519 --> 00:38:42,820
cleared my internship

690
00:38:43,039 --> 00:38:44,440
for winter break.

691
00:38:45,199 --> 00:38:46,019
What's wrong?

692
00:38:47,320 --> 00:38:48,420
Nothing, just a cold.

693
00:38:49,760 --> 00:38:50,739
Here. Sit down.

694
00:38:50,940 --> 00:38:51,440
Sit.

695
00:38:59,460 --> 00:39:00,280
You're burning up,

696
00:39:00,280 --> 00:39:01,199
how can you work?

697
00:39:01,610 --> 00:39:02,422
Where's your family?

698
00:39:02,940 --> 00:39:03,480
I'll call them

699
00:39:03,480 --> 00:39:04,239
to come get you.

700
00:39:07,719 --> 00:39:08,960
Wei Mingzhen is your mom, right?

701
00:39:10,139 --> 00:39:11,440
Don't bother. It's off.

702
00:39:12,300 --> 00:39:13,500
How can it be off?

703
00:39:15,170 --> 00:39:16,222
You had an argument?

704
00:39:17,440 --> 00:39:18,119
Still,

705
00:39:18,119 --> 00:39:19,079
they can't just abandon you.

706
00:39:19,139 --> 00:39:21,360
Hello, who's this?

707
00:39:21,820 --> 00:39:22,360
Hello.

708
00:39:22,880 --> 00:39:24,320
I'm the student counselor

709
00:39:24,440 --> 00:39:25,800
from Jiaohai University.

710
00:39:26,200 --> 00:39:26,844
Are you

711
00:39:26,910 --> 00:39:27,688
- Wei Mingzhen?
- Look,

712
00:39:27,755 --> 00:39:28,222
if this

713
00:39:28,280 --> 00:39:28,911
isn't urgent,

714
00:39:28,955 --> 00:39:30,044
can you call back later?

715
00:39:30,099 --> 00:39:30,980
I'm busy right now.

716
00:40:08,820 --> 00:40:09,420
Wait up!

717
00:40:09,860 --> 00:40:10,340
Hustle!

718
00:40:16,159 --> 00:40:17,039
You okay?

719
00:40:19,380 --> 00:40:20,860
I only have two hours.

720
00:40:21,079 --> 00:40:22,059
Say what you need to say.

721
00:40:23,880 --> 00:40:24,940
Two hours is plenty of time.

722
00:40:24,940 --> 00:40:25,719
No rush.

723
00:40:26,400 --> 00:40:27,420
Walk with me for a bit.

724
00:40:48,000 --> 00:40:50,039
I thought Vineton

725
00:40:51,059 --> 00:40:52,059
would've changed a lot.

726
00:40:53,840 --> 00:40:55,699
I didn't expect these shops to still be here.

727
00:41:00,599 --> 00:41:01,480
There is

728
00:41:01,920 --> 00:41:03,320
this shop on that street

729
00:41:03,579 --> 00:41:03,940
we just

730
00:41:03,940 --> 00:41:04,460
passed...

731
00:41:04,460 --> 00:41:05,539
Do you remember it?

732
00:41:06,500 --> 00:41:07,510
In fifth grade,

733
00:41:07,510 --> 00:41:08,666
you got full score on Chinese and math.

734
00:41:08,840 --> 00:41:09,880
I took you there

735
00:41:09,880 --> 00:41:10,699
for burgers.

736
00:41:11,280 --> 00:41:12,000
Remember?

737
00:41:13,139 --> 00:41:13,659
Yeah.

738
00:41:14,539 --> 00:41:15,579
But back then,

739
00:41:15,579 --> 00:41:16,659
you took a call and left

740
00:41:16,980 --> 00:41:17,980
before finishing.

741
00:41:18,659 --> 00:41:19,940
I walked back alone.

742
00:41:21,119 --> 00:41:22,179
That wasn't the only time.

743
00:41:22,780 --> 00:41:24,460
There was this time when I was in high school,

744
00:41:24,920 --> 00:41:26,139
we met there too.

745
00:41:36,800 --> 00:41:38,280
Just say what you need to say.

746
00:41:38,280 --> 00:41:39,377
Stop beating around the bush.

747
00:41:44,800 --> 00:41:46,420
I just came back to see you.

748
00:41:48,500 --> 00:41:49,155
And?

749
00:41:50,500 --> 00:41:51,780
It's got to be more than that.

750
00:41:56,079 --> 00:41:56,780
That's it.

751
00:42:02,699 --> 00:42:03,420
If you came back

752
00:42:03,420 --> 00:42:04,900
just to say that,

753
00:42:05,539 --> 00:42:06,599
well, you said it.

754
00:42:06,780 --> 00:42:07,659
You've seen me.

755
00:42:08,780 --> 00:42:09,699
You can go now.

756
00:42:11,440 --> 00:42:12,155
Where are you staying?

757
00:42:12,300 --> 00:42:13,420
I'll hail a cab for you.

758
00:42:15,280 --> 00:42:17,099
It hasn't been two hours yet.

759
00:42:21,210 --> 00:42:22,088
Where are you going?
